Description:
AllianceBernstein Holding L.P. (AB) is a global asset management firm providing investment management and research services worldwide to institutional, high-net-worth and retail investors.
AllianceBernstein's headquarters are located in Nashville, Tennessee, in the United States, as well as having locations throughout the world. It has approximately US$581 billion in assets under management as of June 30, 2019. It is 64 percent owned by Equitable Holdings.
